snippet.title: Heroes of Hammerwatch, Moon Temple, Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Moon Temple is the expansion/dlc that brings you all new content to Heroes of Hammerwatch, with a new campaign, hardcore-mode, gameplay-features, and much more.

http://www.heroesofhammerwatch.com

DLC will be avalible on available on Steam and Gog on the 20th FEB 2020.

Crackshell Twitter for faster updates: https://twitter.com/RealCrackshell
